{"type": "article", "id": 28318, "title": "青铜家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-17T06:40:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142450rmynd2lxwig37M0j.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>意大利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.francescofaccin.it/\">Francesco Faccin</a> 为米兰 Nilufar 画廊设计了一套以木质模具铸造的青铜家具 Serial Planks，为青铜与脱蜡工艺的应用开辟了新的可能。与 Faccin 合作的青铜塑件制造商 <a href=\"http://www.fonderiabattaglia.com/en/\">Fonderia Artistica Battaglia</a> 使用了 150 * 7 厘米的整块落叶松木板作为模型，接着倒入熔化的金属以将木材的质感复制进青铜内。在这之后，设计师将一系列可以自由组合的金属板材进行搭配，就创作出了这些实用的家具配置，呈现出了木材的美学和特质。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142446iU6EZygXWK80ahoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142447DbmdEgyzfx3FZOXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021424485UjWBJYrKqT7nE9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142448jRVhm6lQKGsOJwTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}